des: Chris Martin delivers the ultimate destination for legendary tracks that have defined generations, featuring a rich blend of rock, pop, soul, and disco on Classic Hits. Each carefully curated song evokes nostalgia, joy, and inspiration, offering a timeless musical journey through the golden eras. Whether reliving memories or discovering these classics anew, Classic Hits brings the best of yesterday to life, proving that great music only gets better with time.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
